，需照顧母親的日常生活。"},{"pid":"36021808fc40b6f883368e12ed2b7be5e18473eb","tid":1907651,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12370d06a1523419d4ef5964f31b722cde390eb6","tid":1907651,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"推, 警甴正仆街"},{"pid":"f24887fbb8cf869a32a76acc831d5ace00233789","tid":1907651,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199c96c40e1d62724099628eae00424153144592","tid":1907651,"uid":91595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e89a4c29045cffd5f9d2a53bd3480b9a62088bf","tid":1907651,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b984947ef29929534521f28ceb98bde7554bd1","tid":1907651,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:58:07.000Z","msg":"你班黑法<br />\n係唔係屌人老母好撚過癮？"},{"pid":"def4f2f9ce8877e5edd85c4b972ceb5e011bf6db","tid":1907651,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor